// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2301 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: fe0321f2-d381-5d15-b320-92f605603e0b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
